# Naming Convention - MoonProject

## 1. Classes & Structs

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| MonoBehaviour | PascalCase + suffix mô tả | `FarmSlot`, `AnimalController`, `QuestPanel` |
| ScriptableObject Manager | PascalCase + `Controller`/`Manager` | `DataController`, `AudioManager` |
| Data Wrapper | `DataWrapper` + tên entity | `DataWrapperItem`, `DataWrapperPlant` |
| Config Wrapper | `ConfigWrapper` + tên entity | `ConfigWrapperAnimal`, `ConfigWrapperLevel` |
| UI Popup | PascalCase + `Popup`/`Panel`/`UI` | `CardCollectionPopup`, `ShopPanel`, `CraftingUI` |
| Data Model | PascalCase + `State`/`Data` | `FarmState`, `LeaderboardData` |
| Enum | PascalCase (singular) | `CardRarity`, `TeeMessageType` |

## 2. Methods

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| Public method | PascalCase | `Initialize()`, `Show()`, `ForceComplete()` |
| Private method | PascalCase | `UpdateUI()`, `HandleMessage()` |
| Event handler | `OnClick` / `OnComplete` + action | `OnClickClose()`, `OnCompletePurchase()` |
| Coroutine | `IE` prefix hoặc tên mô tả | `IECountDown()`, `ShowPopupWithDelay()` |
| Bool getter | `Is`/`Has`/`Can` prefix | `IsReady`, `HasPlant`, `CanHarvest` |

## 3. Fields & Properties

| Loại | Pattern | Ví dụ |
|------|---------|-------|
| [SerializeField] private | camelCase | `txtTimer`, `btnClose`, `popup` |
| Private field | camelCase hoặc `_` prefix | `_state`, `eventData`, `growCoroutine` |
| Public property | PascalCase | `PlantId`, `CurrentGameData`, `Index` |
| Constant | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE hoặc PascalCase | `ENERGY_ID`, `MaxRetryCount` |
| Static readonly | PascalCase | `Wait1s`, `DefaultTimeout` |

## 4. UI Component Prefix

| Prefix | Component | Ví dụ |
|--------|-----------|-------|
| `txt` | TextMeshProUGUI | `txtLevel`, `txtCountDown` |
| `btn` | Button | `btnClose`, `btnConfirm` |
| `img` | Image | `imgAvatar`, `imgIcon` |
| `go` | GameObject | `goRewardPanel`, `goLoading` |
| `anim` | Animator | `animPopup`, `animCard` |
| `cg` | CanvasGroup | `cgOverlay` |

## 5. Folders & Files

- File name = Class name (1:1)
- Folder dùng PascalCase: `GridObjects`, `CardCollection`, `SideQuest`
- Subfolder theo feature, không theo type

## 6. Constants & IDs

- Item IDs: format `"ss_XXX"` (đã có trong `Constants.ID`)
- Scene names: `"MAP_{id}"`, `"LOADING"`, `"Splash"`
- Message types: thêm vào `TeeMessageType` enum
- PlayerPref keys: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE trong `PlayerPrefController`

---

### Ví dụ ĐÚNG

```csharp
namespace DreamyHarvest.UI
{
    public class DailyRewardPopup : BasePopup<DailyRewardPopup>
    {
        [SerializeField] private TextMeshProUGUI txtTitle;
        [SerializeField] private Button btnClaim;
        [SerializeField] private GameObject goRewardContainer;

        private DailyRewardController _controller;
        private bool _isClaimed;

        public bool IsClaimed => _isClaimed;

        public void Initialize(DailyRewardController controller)
        {
            _controller = controller;
            UpdateUI();
        }

        private void OnClickClaim()
        {
            if (_isClaimed) return;
            _controller.ClaimReward();
            _isClaimed = true;
        }
    }
}
```

### Ví dụ SAI

```csharp
public class daily_reward_popup : BasePopup<daily_reward_popup> // snake_case class
{
    public TextMeshProUGUI Title; // Public, PascalCase cho field
    public Button claimButton; // Không có prefix btn
    [SerializeField] private GameObject reward_container; // snake_case field

    DailyRewardController m_controller; // m_ prefix
    bool claimed; // Thiếu access modifier

    public bool getClaimed() { return claimed; } // Method thay vì property, camelCase

    void click_claim() // snake_case method
    {
        m_controller.ClaimReward();
    }
}
```
